s-c42-Rio_de_Janeiro_State_of_Rio_de_Janeiro.html" class="BMQDV _F Gv wSSLS SwZTJ EabUM FGwzt ukgoS"><span class="mzjtg n q jOVtB NZDrh"><span class="biGQs _P avBIb navcl">Tours en Río de Janeiro</span></span></a></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https:\u002F\u002Fschema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FTourism-g13-South_America-Vacations.html","name":"Am\u00E9rica del Sur"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"item":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FTourism-g294280-Brazil-Vacations.html","name":"Brasil"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"item":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FTourism-g303488-State_of_Rio_de_Janeiro-Vacations.html","name":"Estado de R\u00EDo de Janeiro (RJ)"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":4,"item":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FTourism-g303506-Rio_de_Janeiro_State_of_Rio_de_Janeiro-Vacations.html","name":"R\u00EDo de Janeiro"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":5,"item":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FAttractions-g303506-Activities-Rio_de_Janeiro_State_of_Rio_de_Janeiro.html","name":"Atracciones en R\u00EDo de Janeiro"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":6,"name":"Tours en R\u00EDo de Janeiro"}]}</script></div></div></div><div class="hJiTo z"><div class="IDaDx mvTrV cyIij fluiI SMjpI Iwmxp"><div></div><header class="MEOcJ e"><div></div><div class="aFwgl"><div class="Pw"><div class="JvPzm f u rtsNV"><div class="F1" data-automation="breadcrumbs-header"><a href="/ClientLink?value=ZjZ4Xy9BdHRyYWN0aW9uX1Byb2R1Y3RzLWczMDM1MDYtUmlvX2RlX0phbmVpcm9fU3RhdGVfb2ZfUmlvX2RlX0phbmVpcm8uaHRtbF9jSVE%3D" class="BMQDV _F Gv wSSLS SwZTJ EabUM FGwzt ukgoS"><div class="biGQs _P VImYz AWdfh"><div class="f u"><div class="PW"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" height="22px" class="d Vb UmNoP" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16.6 5.65-6.4 6.4 6.4 6.3-1.4 1.4-7.8-7.7 7.8-7.8z"></path></svg></div><div class="Wb">Mira todas las cosas que hacer en Río de Janeiro</div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="mmBWG u"><div class="ycuCc"></div></div></header></div><div><div data-automation="poi-jsonld"><script type="application/ld+json">{"@type":"Product","productID":"25334026","sku":"25334026","mpn":"25334026","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FAttractionProductReview-g303506-d25334026-Maracana_Stadium_Match_Tickets_with_Welcome_Drink-Rio_de_Janeiro_State_of_Rio_de_J.html","name":"Estadio Maracan\u00E1: entradas para el partido con bebida de bienvenida","aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"5.0","reviewCount":22},"description":"Comenzaremos nuestra aventura en el famoso Maracan\u00E1, un hist\u00F3rico y c\u00E9lebre estadio de f\u00FAtbol. Este lugar ic\u00F3nico fue el escenario del infame 'Maracanazo' en 1950, donde Uruguay sorprendi\u00F3 a Brasil para ganar la Copa del Mundo, fue testigo de la cuarta victoria de Alemania en la Copa del Mundo en 2014 y es donde Pel\u00E9 anot\u00F3 su gol n\u00FAmero 1.000.\n\nNuestro viaje comienza con una reuni\u00F3n previa al partido para conectar con otros fan\u00E1ticos del f\u00FAtbol. Nos reuniremos en una plaza vibrante, llena de bares animados, donde los seguidores locales se re\u00FAnen para intercambiar historias y generar expectaci\u00F3n por el juego. Esta es tu oportunidad de sumergirte en la escena del f\u00FAtbol local y conocer a otros entusiastas.\n\nA continuaci\u00F3n, nos uniremos a los apasionados seguidores que se dirigen al estadio. Le aseguraremos asientos que le permitir\u00E1n sumergirse por completo en la vibrante atm\u00F3sfera, brind\u00E1ndole una verdadera muestra de la pasi\u00F3n local. Ya sea Flamengo, Fluminense o cualquier otro equipo en acci\u00F3n, estar\u00E1s justo en medio de la emoci\u00F3n, \u00A1especialmente durante un emocionante derbi local!","image":"https:\u002F\u002Fdynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com\u002Fmedia\u002Fphoto-o\u002F29\u002Fd8\u002F06\u002Fae\u002Fcaption.jpg?w=1200&h=-1&s=1","brand":{"@type":"Brand","name":"Rio As A Local"},"@context":"https:\u002F\u002Fschema.org","review":[{"@type":"Review","name":"10\u002F10 experience","datePublished":"2026-04-10","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"christophermV5832LX"},"reviewBody":"Davi was amazing, a real Flamengo die hard and all round football fan. Felt like we got an authentic experience from start to finish and an amazing result to match. Couldn\u2019t recommend this experience any higher, the flamengo fans are next level."},{"@type":"Review","name":"Goal!!!!!","datePublished":"2026-04-02","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Patricia F"},"reviewBody":"I would like to thank our guide Yan for such an exhilarating experience. The whole process was made simple, without the tour I could see how this would be overwhelming. The meetup location was perfect, the area was easy to find, lively and safe. We then headed in an authentic adventure. A closeup view of a game day experience. Yan explained the many layers of the game and background knowledge of the stadium and the fan base. We stopped and were able to take in the whole vibe with our welcome drink. After. A brief food stop, we headed into the stadium. Yan directed us through the entire process. We had great seats and loved watching the game. At the end of the night we were escorted back to our meetup point."},{"@type":"Review","name":"Don\u2019t miss this .. You\u2019ll Regret It","datePublished":"2025-10-04","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"calistaguas"},"reviewBody":"If I had to pick one excursion to do in Rio this is it! Our tour guide Evan and Ian were such a blast to be with, they were super knowledgeable with any questions about the game or culture in Rio. They made us so comfortable, communication was smooth, and the vibes were immaculate! Even if you don\u2019t like futebol go for the experience of being surrounded by the Brazilian culture. Get the a\u00E7a\u00ED and chips, not much of a beer fan but this I could the beer here I can drink. Trust me you do not want to miss out!!!"},{"@type":"Review","name":"Amazing Experience","datePublished":"2025-08-10","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"nadjaelizabethm"},"reviewBody":"Amazing experience - can highly recommend this tour. \nEvan was a great guide and led us to our section in the legendary Maracan\u00E3-Stadion. Wouldn\u2019t want to search my way around there by myself\u2026. The atmosphere during the match was just fantastic!  A highlight for every football fan and certainly a highlight of our holiday. \nWe went as a family with two kids and always felt completely safe. Thank you Evan!"},{"@type":"Review","name":"Amazing experience","datePublished":"2025-07-18","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"CHUA W"},"reviewBody":"Evan guide us well from gathering spot to stadium. I did enjoy the whole trip to maracana stadium. The atmosphere was amazing and its safe."},{"@type":"Review","name":"Must do at least once in life","datePublished":"2025-07-13","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dream26431192690"},"reviewBody":"Unique experience being in the middle of the fans. The guide was kind, supportive and helpful. He did care about us. The drink included ate very appropiately as you really need them due to the heat after walking an enter into the stadium. He waited until all of us got a cab, back to our hotel."},{"@type":"Review","name":"Perfect for everyone who loves football","datePublished":"2024-11-14","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"230maximiliand"},"reviewBody":"For everyone who loves the Game of Football, watching a match at the Maracana is an absolute Must. Our Trip was very well planned, so that we always felt safe in and around the stadium.\nI really recommend this Tour.\nObrigado!"},{"@type":"Review","name":"An Unforgettable experience!","datePublished":"2023-10-10","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Andreas T"},"reviewBody":"The chants, the atmosphere, the passion it was amazing, creating goosebumps!!\nHowever, little feedback, the pregame meetup could have been better for the price of the package! I mean the money totally worth it but a bit overpriced since apart for the meetup point, the one beer offered and walking safely to the stadium, the package is too high as game ticket is cheap! Gustavo, a Fluminese super fan for life, our guide, though, was very cool and helpful all the time! \nAnyway i loved the experience overall! A must thing to do in Rio!"},{"@type":"Review","name":"Amazing experience, we loved every minute!","datePublished":"2023-07-26","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"J1295SKangelab"},"reviewBody":"What an experience!  If you love futbol, this is a must do event while in Rio de Janiero!  Bruno is a true Flamengo fan & made the afternoon a safe, fun time!  He was clear in his directions where to meet & ensured we had great seats & stayed with us the entire match.  The Flamengo fans are intense, fun & friendly.  Be sure to wear your red & black!!  "},{"@type":"Review","name":"INCREDIBLE EXPERIENCE AT THE MARACAN\u00C3!","datePublished":"2023-06-27","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"JMB1603"},"reviewBody":"Bruno and Gustavo ensured we had a great time watching their team, Fluminense, play at the Maracan\u00E3. They met us at a bar close to the stadium along with other tourists, buying us all a drink before the game. They then took us to the stadium, finding us seats right within the loudest and most passionate fans to get the best experience. Watching the football in that atmosphere was incredible! After the game the made sure we got to the metro safely, they really looked after us at all points during the evening. I would highly recommend for any football fans or even if you're not, you'll still have a fantastic time. \u26BD"}],"offers":{"@type":"Offer","url":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tripadvisor.cl\u002FAttractionProductReview-g303506-d25334026-Maracana_Stadium_Match_Tickets_with_Welcome_Drink-Rio_de_Janeiro_State_of_Rio_de_J.html","price":89386,"priceCurrency":"CLP","availability":"https:\u002F\u002Fschema.org\u002FInStock"}}</script></div><div class="Skses z vECdA"><div class="xfLuN"><div class="C" data-ft="true"><div data-fixed-header="true" class="CtwUQ D _U l Gi uwyUa t"><div class="yfjGj f O k NWilY"><div class="QqwMf f u w"><div class="f I" data-automation="sticky-breadcrumbs-header"><div class="biGQs _P ezezH"><a href="/ClientLink?value=ZjZ4Xy9BdHRyYWN0aW9uX1Byb2R1Y3RzLWczMDM1MDYtUmlvX2RlX0phbmVpcm9fU3RhdGVfb2ZfUmlvX2RlX0phbmVpcm8uaHRtbF9jSVE%3D" class="BMQDV _F Gv wSSLS SwZTJ FGwzt ukgoS"><div class="biGQs _P VImYz AWdfh"><div class="f u"><div class="PW"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" height="22px" class="d Vb UmNoP" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16.6 5.65-6.4 6.4 6.4 6.3-1.4 1.4-7.8-7.7 7.8-7.8z"></path></svg></div>Mira todas las cosas que hacer en Río de Janeiro</div></div></a></div></div><div class="QaHqF f u"><div class="biGQs _P alXOW oCpZu GzNcM nvOhm UTQMg ZTpaU ezezH"><span>Estadio Maracaná: entradas para el partido con bebida de bienvenida</span></div><div class="biGQs _P ezezH"><span class="mOLoX f"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em" height="1em" class="d Vb pNwxT" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 19.99a7.99 7.99 0 1 0 0-15.98 7.99 7.99 0 0 0 0 15.98"></path></svg>5</span></div><div class="iVWIq f"><div class="f u"><button class="BrOJk u j z _F _S wSSLS tIqAi iNBVo" type="button"><span class="kLqdM"><span class="biGQs _P ezezH"><div class="HMZEw"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" height="24px" class="d Vb UmNoP" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M3.798 5.166A5.77 5.77 0 0 1 7.72 3.63c1.455 0 2.857.548 3.922 1.536l.005.005.341.322.332-.317a5.77 5.77 0 0 1 3.928-1.54c1.458 0 2.862.55 3.928 1.54l.004.004c1.093 1.032 1.598 2.324 1.569 3.662-.03 1.323-.579 2.643-1.5 3.785-.884 1.096-2.85 2.943-4.547 4.478a185 185 0 0 1-3.153 2.785l-.069.059-.489-.569.489.569-.485.416-.488-.412a102 102 0 0 1-7.75-7.288l-.021-.021-.02-.023c-1.725-2.115-2.203-5.32.08-7.453zm8.19 13.