e.%20Yan%20explained%20the%20many%20layers%20of%20the%20game%20and%20background%20knowledge%20of%20the%20stadium%20and%20the%20fan%20base.%20We%20stopped%20and%20were%20able%20to%20take%20in%20the%20whole%20vibe%20with%20our%20welcome%20drink.%20After.%20A%20brief%20food%20stop%2C%20we%20headed%20into%20the%20stadium.%20Yan%20directed%20us%20through%20the%20entire%20process.%20We%20had%20great%20seats%20and%20loved%20watching%20the%20game.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20night%20we%20were%20escorted%20back%20to%20our%20meetup%20point.%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%7D%2C%7B%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%40type%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22Review%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22name%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22Don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20this%20..%20You%E2%80%99ll%20Regret%20It%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22datePublished%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%222025-10-04%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22author%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%7B%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%40type%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22Person%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22name%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22calistaguas%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%7D%2C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22reviewBody%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%5C%22If%20I%20had%20to%20pick%20one%20excursion%20to%20do%20in%20Rio%20this%20is%20it!%20Our%20tour%20guide%20Evan%20and%20Ian%20were%20such%20a%20blast%20to%20be%20with%2C%20they%20were%20super%20knowledgeable%20with%20any%20questions%20about%20the%20game%20or%20culture%20in%20Rio.%20They%20made%20us%20so%20comfortable%2C%20communication%20was%20smooth%2C%20and%20the%20vibes%20were%20immaculate!%20Even%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20futebol%20go%20for%20the%20experience%20of%20being%20surrounded%20by%20the%20Brazilian%20culture.%20Get%20the%20a%C3%A7a%C3%AD%20and%20chips%2C%20not%20much%20of%20a%20beer%20fan%20but%20this%20I%20coul