ue%20claro%20en%20sus%20instrucciones%20sobre%20d%C3%B3nde%20encontrarnos%20y%20se%20asegur%C3%B3%20de%20que%20tuvi%C3%A9ramos%20buenos%20asientos%20y%20se%20qued%C3%B3%20con%20nosotros%20durante%20todo%20el%20partido.%20Los%20fans%20de%20Flamengo%20son%20intensos%2C%20divertidos%20y%20simp%C3%A1ticos.%20%C2%A1Aseg%C3%BArate%20de%20usar%20tu%20rojo%20y%20negro!%20!%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%22username%5C%5C%5C%22%3Anull%2C%5C%5C%5C%22connectionToSubject%5C%5C%5C%22%3Anull%2C%5C%5C%5C%22mgmtResponse%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%7B%5C%5C%5C%22id%5C%5C%5C%22%3A916428473%2C%5C%5C%5C%22text%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%22We're%20thrilled%20to%20hear%20that%20you%20had%20an%20amazing%20time%20at%20the%20futbol%20match%20with%20Bruno%20as%20your%20guide!%20It's%20fantastic%20to%20know%20that%20you%20enjoyed%20the%20experience%20and%20felt%20safe%20and%20well-guided%20throughout.%20Bruno's%20passion%20for%20Flamengo%20truly%20shines%20through%2C%20and%20we're%20lucky%20to%20have%20him%20on%20our%20team.%5C%5C%5C%5Cn%5C%5C%5C%5CnThe%20vibrant%20atmosphere%20created%20by%20Flamengo%20fans%20is%20something%20truly%20special%2C%20and%20we're%20delighted%20that%20you%20found%20them%20intense%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20friendly.%20Wearing%20the%20red%20and%20black%20colors%20is%20indeed%20a%20great%20way%20to%20immerse%20yourself%20in%20the%20excitement!%5C%5C%5C%5Cn%5C%5C%5C%5CnThank%20you%20for%20choosing%20us%20for%20your%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%20futbol%20experience.%20We%20hope%20to%20welcome%20you%20back%20for%20more%20unforgettable%20moments%20in%20the%20future.%5C%5C%5C%5Cn%5C%5C%5C%5CnBest%20regards%2C%5C%5C%5C%5CnBruno%20-%20Rio%20as%20a%20Local%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%22language%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%22en%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%22translationType%5C%5C%5C%22%3Anull%2C%5C%5C%5C%22publishedDate%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%222023-09-13%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%22connectionToSubject%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5C%5C%22Owner%5C%5C%5C%22%2C%5C%5C%5C%22userProfile%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%7B%5C%5C%5C%22userId%5C%5C%5C%22%3A%5C%5